        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are adjacent to an ally.</p><hr /><p>You learned that supporting members of your pair or pod also makes you stronger. You join hands with an adjacent willing ally, which occupies one of each of your hands. For 1 round, while you remain adjacent to that ally and holding hands, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC. Additionally, you and your ally gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your saving throws against attempts to [[/act demoralize]], [[/act reposition]], [[/act shove]], or [[/act trip]] either of you.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Hold Hands]</p>"
